# VIBE:GENERATED {{VIBE_VERSION}}
# ── JBS Vibe Editing — API keys ──────────────────────────────────────
# This file is a TEMPLATE (safe to commit). Your real keys go into `.env`
# (created from this file at init — never committed), or use the UI's
# API Keys page, which edits .env for you and can test each key.
# Keys stay on YOUR machine and are only ever sent to the provider they
# belong to. See SECURITY notes in the project README.

# REQUIRED — transcription (word-level captions) + AI thumbnails.
# Get one: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Rough cost: a few cents per video (whisper-1 + gpt-image-2).
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# REQUIRED — the visual QA "eyes" (Gemini video review / council / reference analysis).
# Get one: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Rough cost: cents per review pass (gemini-3.1-flash-lite).
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# REQUIRED — AI voice-over, music and sound effects.
# Get one: https://elevenlabs.io → your profile → API Keys.
# Uses your ElevenLabs subscription credits.
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# OPTIONAL — paid AI video generation via Runway (Gen-4.5 / Gen-4 Turbo / Aleph).
# Leave empty to skip — everything else works without it.
# Get one: https://dev.runwayml.com · Rough cost: ~$0.13–0.38 per generated second.
RUNWAY_API_SECRET=

# OPTIONAL — paid AI video generation via Seedance (fal.ai).
# Leave empty to skip. Get one: https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
# Rough cost: ~$0.04 per generated second.
FAL_KEY=
